description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if during Week 2 of the 2024-25 NFL Season all of the following occurs;

-In the game between the New York Giants and the Washington Commanders, Daniel Jones records one or more turnovers (either an interception or a fumble recovered by the Commanders)

-In the game between the Kansas City Chiefs and the Cincinnati Bengals, Travis Kelce records 40 or more receiving yards

-In the game between the Chicago Bears and Houston Texans, Caleb Williams records one or more touchdowns (rushing, receiving, or passing)

-In the game between the Philadelphia Eagles and Atalanta Falcons, Kirk Cousins records 5 or more rushing yards

Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If a relevant game is canceled or postponed beyond September 18, this market will resolve to "No".

The resolution source will be ESPN.com.
